1. Clone the Repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/your-username/liv2train-backend.git
cd liv2train-backend


2. Set Up PostgreSQL Database

Install PostgreSQL
Create a database named liv2train.
Open src/main/resources/application.properties and set your PostgreSQL credentials:

properties
Copy code
spring.datasource.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/liv2train
spring.datasource.username=postgres
spring.datasource.password=your_password
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
spring.jpa.show-sql=true
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.dialect=org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQLDialect

3. Build and Run the Application

Open the Project in your IDE

Run the Application:

In IntelliJ IDEA:

Right-click on Liv2TrainApplication.java.
Select Run 'Liv2TrainApplication'.
In Eclipse:

Right-click on your project.
Select Run As â†’ Spring Boot App.


4. Test the APIs

Using Postman:
Test the POST API (/api/v1/training-centers):

URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/training-centers

Method: POST

Headers:

Content-Type: application/json
Body (raw JSON):

json
Copy code
{
  "centerName": "ABC Training Center",
  "centerCode": "ABC123456789",
  "address": {
    "detailedAddress": "123 Main St",
    "city": "CityName",
    "state": "StateName",
    "pincode": "123456"
  },
  "studentCapacity": 100,
  "coursesOffered": ["Java", "Spring"],
  "contactEmail": "info@abctraining.com",
  "contactPhone": "9876543210"
}
Expected Response:

Status Code: 201 Created

Body:

json
Copy code
{
  "id": 1,
  "centerName": "ABC Training Center",
  "centerCode": "ABC123456789",
  "address": {
    "detailedAddress": "123 Main St",
    "city": "CityName",
    "state": "StateName",
    "pincode": "123456"
  },
  "studentCapacity": 100,
  "coursesOffered": ["Java", "Spring"],
  "createdOn": 1694095200000,
  "contactEmail": "info@abctraining.com",
  "contactPhone": "9876543210"
}
Test the GET API (/api/v1/training-centers):

URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/training-centers

Method: GET

Expected Response:

Status Code: 200 OK

Body:

json
Copy code
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "centerName": "ABC Training Center",
    "centerCode": "ABC123456789",
    "address": {
      "detailedAddress": "123 Main St",
      "city": "CityName",
      "state": "StateName",
      "pincode": "123456"
    },
    "studentCapacity": 100,
    "coursesOffered": ["Java", "Spring"],
    "createdOn": 1694095200000,
    "contactEmail": "info@abctraining.com",
    "contactPhone": "9876543210"
  }
]
